  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Collect Sac Venom from rare <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Land Urchins</span> found occasionally on planets.<br>Harvesting may require a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Haz-Mat Gauntlet</span>. Recruit a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Base Armorer</span> to learn the blueprint.<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">WARNING:</span> Land Urchins have spine-based defenses.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从偶尔能在星球上找到的稀有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">陆生海胆</span>中收集囊袋毒液。<br>采集过程可能需要使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">防护手套</span>。招募一名<span class=\"name name-technology\">基地军械士</span>来学习设计图。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告：</span>陆生海胆有脊刺保护。",
    "TencentChinese": "从偶尔能在星球上找到的稀有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">陆生海胆</span>中收集萨克毒液。<br>采集过程可能需要使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">防护手套</span>。招募一名<span class=\"name name-technology\">基地军械士</span>来学习设计图。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告：</span>陆生海胆有脊刺保护。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從偶爾能在星球上找到的稀有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海膽仙人掌</span>中收集囊袋毒液。<br>採收過程可能需要使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">防護手套</span>。招募一名<span class=\"name name-technology\">基地軍械士</span>來學習設計圖。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告：</span>海膽仙人掌有脊刺保護。"
